snippet.title: BM Sculptures
snippet.description:
Catch me on Season 3 of NBC's  "Making It" - now streaming on Hulu and Peacock TV

 My name is Blake McFarland and I am a retired professional baseball player (2011-2018 Toronto Blue Jays) turned full time artist and maker. I specialize in using recycled and mixed materials to create custom sculptures and interactions for clients. I am falling more in love with woodworking and metalworking and many of my videos show my love for this new form. 

If you like my content please subscribe, it helps support me so I can keep making weekly videos. 

Have an idea and want to see it turn into reality? Shoot me an email through my website.

Check out my website at www.blakemcfarland.com
Instagram & Facebook @Bmsculptures
